modName: Billyro's Armory - List and Locations Sheet
summary: A list of Billyro's weapon and some armor mods with information on how and/or where to get them. File is in Excel format.
descriptionHtml:
[size=4]This is a small list of [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1734939?tab=user+files&BH=1]Billyro's [/url]weapon (and armor) mods that contains pictures alongside the names and collected information from mod pages on how and/or where to get them. File is in Excel format.



[i]This will probably be updated from time to time when Billyro uploads another mod that you need to keep tabs on where to find it/them.[/i][/size]
author: Billyro and Vilidran
